headline: SOLV Q2 Deep Dive: Product Launches and Execution Drive Outperformance Amid Margin Pressures
summary: Healthcare solutions provider Solventum (NYSE:SOLV) reported revenue ahead of Wall Street’s expectations in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 3.8% year on year to $2.16 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.69 per share was 16.3% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
